		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If the top Address line was wrong, that does NOT mean there would be more glitches, it ALL depends on how you would use the ROM, and it looks like with the splits, the graphics change, and would cause corruption when trying to switch to another graphics page higher in ROM.<br /><br />Graphics problems, 100%. I'm not really asking anybody, I'm just letting you know so he gets his problem traced faster.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
