	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The Ninja Gaiden II intro sequence shows the IRQs happening much later than they should.<br /><br />It could be a problem with PPU A12 not staying low long enough. It could be some sort of capacitance on /IRQ. It could be interference on M2 causing the MMC3 to miss some (but not all) scanlines.<br /><br />These are what I can think of based on the video and a quick look at the MMC3 documentation.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
